  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/4a655ee075a62687746aba0a2bc6074e.avif?t=1745874665\" width=592 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Breaker is a twin-stick beat 'em up set within the Nexus Orion Labs corporate compound. You were hired as a product tester for the all-new \"Breaker Fists,\" but after a chance encounter and a paperwork mix-up, you'll have to unravel the secrets of your employer and take them down once and for all. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/07061c91b9715f78ba5db925d01130ae.avif?t=1745874665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras_big/07061c91b9715f78ba5db925d01130ae.avif?t=1745874665 width=800 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b914424366a6c2f249fdd47917ba6d8f.poster.avif?t=1745874665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b914424366a6c2f249fdd47917ba6d8f.webm?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b914424366a6c2f249fdd47917ba6d8f.mp4?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Many of life’s problems can be fixed by punching things.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your journey begins by testing the all-new “Breaker Fists.” Soon, you'll adapt, evolve, and punch through a dynamic, colorful world full of strange friends and even more relentless enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/7b32cfd14e7104aa5ff5d5fb2d161b98.avif?t=1745874665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras_big/7b32cfd14e7104aa5ff5d5fb2d161b98.avif?t=1745874665 width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/6f12dc1153e56002c1fee3d32957f544.poster.avif?t=1745874665\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/6f12dc1153e56002c1fee3d32957f544.webm?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/6f12dc1153e56002c1fee3d32957f544.mp4?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Fight Together or Die Together</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 people total in couch co-op local multiplayer in randomly generated arenas in the Infinite Arena game mode. Just how long can your crew survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b519cab357c282ae143082d9193c8b38.avif?t=1745874665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras_big/b519cab357c282ae143082d9193c8b38.avif?t=1745874665 width=800 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/4397522a66195b8f9d896504ca7c8238.poster.avif?t=1745874665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/4397522a66195b8f9d896504ca7c8238.webm?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/4397522a66195b8f9d896504ca7c8238.mp4?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Your boss would rather you not…</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a paperwork mix-up, you’re nearly murdered for an “unforgivable error,” after which you make it your mission to take down your employer and escape their corporate compound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/9ca08dc35ad8dd7e031812de84b89888.avif?t=1745874665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras_big/9ca08dc35ad8dd7e031812de84b89888.avif?t=1745874665 width=800 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/59082835c00d65abe1f43c6160902a4e.poster.avif?t=1745874665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/59082835c00d65abe1f43c6160902a4e.webm?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/59082835c00d65abe1f43c6160902a4e.mp4?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Much more than snacks and drinks!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use vending machines to purchase upgrades, temporary boosts of power, or assistants to help you on your journey.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/4a655ee075a62687746aba0a2bc6074e.avif?t=1745874665\" width=592 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Breaker is a twin-stick beat 'em up set within the Nexus Orion Labs corporate compound. You were hired as a product tester for the all-new \"Breaker Fists,\" but after a chance encounter and a paperwork mix-up, you'll have to unravel the secrets of your employer and take them down once and for all. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/07061c91b9715f78ba5db925d01130ae.avif?t=1745874665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras_big/07061c91b9715f78ba5db925d01130ae.avif?t=1745874665 width=800 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b914424366a6c2f249fdd47917ba6d8f.poster.avif?t=1745874665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b914424366a6c2f249fdd47917ba6d8f.webm?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/b914424366a6c2f249fdd47917ba6d8f.mp4?t=1745874665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Many of life’s problems can be fixed by punching things.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_